==Welcome
au3 wiki is a minimalist wiki engine in pure php. It provides basic wiki functionality in a small codebase.
The default password for editing pages is '!!password!!'. Please change this in !!index.php!!!
You can use the {{http://au3.org/utils/pwgen.php|password tool}} to generate your own password hash.
===Features
.Minimalist
.Filesystem based (no databases)
.Easy to use {markup|markup}
.{themes|Themeable}
.{plugins|Plugin support}
.Engine uses no javascript/cookies
===Acknowledgements
.Some code adapted from Felix Plesoianu's {{http://felix.plesoianu.ro/php/wabisabi/|wabisabi wiki}}
